Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.03,0:02:04.10,OPCN,,0,0,0,,漆黑昏暗的街道 無數明亮窗戶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.10,0:02:08.04,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}都是被裝飾過的外表
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.25,0:02:14.57,OPCN,,0,0,0,,沉重的枷鎖 纏繞在蒼白的頸上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.57,0:02:18.81,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}嘲笑著世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.51,0:02:22.12,OPCN,,0,0,0,,[Everything reflects the darkness]
